data.description: Location, Location, Location! Welcome to this stunning Shenandoah home, a turnkey short-term rental gem with a lush backyard and heated oasis pool. Earning over $90,000, it boasts 2 bedrooms, a den and 1 bath. Modern amenities, a marble-tiled bath, central air, and a new motor gate provide luxury and privacy. Additional den/office space not included in the current square footage. Total living space is 1,120 sq ft. Near Brickell, Coral Gables, and Coconut Grove, it provides easy access to Key Biscayne, Miami Beach, and Downtown, with proximity to I-95 and 836. Zoned T3R, allows expansion and multi-level. Owners rerouted plumbing and electrical to the garage for easy conversion. Don't miss this luxury and convenience schedule a viewing today! Buyer verify all information
